samo za smejanje.

136
00:13:28,689 --> 00:13:31,889
Posle nekog vremena, to će
postati deo vas.

137
00:13:53,290 --> 00:13:54,990
Izvinite.

138
00:14:10,590 --> 00:14:13,591
Hej ispala vam je hemijska.

139
00:14:23,391 --> 00:14:25,091
Quidnunc.

140
00:14:26,691 --> 00:14:28,591
Quidnunc?

141
00:14:33,491 --> 00:14:36,691
