želi sve da zna.

142
00:14:43,292 --> 00:14:44,392
Čime mogu da vas uslužim?

143
00:14:44,692 --> 00:14:46,992
Za mene "sedam i sedam",

144
00:14:47,292 --> 00:14:50,292
